        "content": "<p>that sounded promising but I couldn't figure out how to do it; concretely,  I have </p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">have</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">eq_h</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">∀</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">u</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">v</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">V</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">μ_v</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">G</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">u</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">μ_v</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">G</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">v</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">by</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">exact</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">fun</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">u</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">v</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">↦</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">vt_avg_dist_from_vertex_eq</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">G</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hconn</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">u</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">v</span>\n\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"k\">have</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">p</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">∑</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">v</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">V</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">μ_v</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">G</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">v</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Fintype</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">card</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">V</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">μ_v</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">G</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">u</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">by</span>\n<span class=\"w\">     </span><span class=\"n\">apply</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">constant_sum</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">λ</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">V</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">μ_v</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">G</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">u</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">eq_h</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>and I'm trying to replace the application of constant_sum (defined in the OP) by a call to <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/find/?pattern=Finset.sum_eq_card_nsmul#doc\">docs#Finset.sum_eq_card_nsmul</a>, but couldn't figure out how to do it</p>",
